title: Thousands March Near Mar-a-Lago to Protest Trump
text: Thousands March Near Mar-a-Lago to Protest Trump About three thousand demonstrators have marched near President Donald Trump's Florida estate to protest his now-blocked executive order temporarily limiting immigration.
